<descript>
<abstract>Turks and Caicos Islands, 1985 is a scanned map of the Caribbean country Turks and Caicos Islands at a scale of 25,000. The map is comprised with sixteen sheets and georeferenced to the surface of the earth and fit to World Geodetic System (1984) coordinates. The original scanned file with additional information is also provided.</abstract>
<purpose>Scanned maps may be used for a variety of purposes. This image may be used in a GIS.</purpose>
</descript>
